	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.15]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>ATTN: I AM NOT trying to say Iksar are better than other races.  But, here is why i love my Iksar necro.  REGEN.  hehe thats it.  well also cause he looks so bad @ss but...Forage is ok, Swimmin is kewl, and the ac is nice but Regen rules when u have mana disease.  If u dont believe me go ask a druid to regen ya and watch how mana disease doesnt hurt anymore.  This is what it is always like for a iksar.  Only problem we face is the low int that iksar have but that not much of a problem considering how cheap int items can be.  And iksar are beloved in their homeland and velious so the so called disadvantage of the fleshies not liking us is bogus.  Plus the best zones for necros are on Kunark.  FoB, Kurns, Loio, WW, OT and boom u are 40. never even had to go more than 1 zone away from cabilis. Dalnir is very easy for us iksar to get to and very easy for a necro to solo and a source of wealth, then u have Kurns which is bone chips heaven.  When u get 40 u can pretty much do what ever u want and velious is always welcome to iksar.  Of course all this is just my opinion.  =) i would love to hear of some opposing ideas as long as they are clean and not flames.  <br>&nbsp;<br>Fendrish 48 Barb War<br>Deadinc 38 Iksar Necro<br>Zebriz 12 Iksar Shaman</td></tr>
