	   <tr><td colspan=2>Necros have 6 or maybe 7  dots that stack. 1)Darkness line, 2)Boil Blood line, 3)Heart Flutter line, 4)Venom of the Snake, 5)Vampiric Curse, 6) Infectious Cloud, 7) dont know if there is nother or not, havent experimented enough.  I do know that the first 6 all stack nicely.  I know that we can stack other spells on mob too such as wave of enfeeblment and shadow vortex and have no problems.  But they debuffs. Umm for starting necro, moonstone rings rock.  str and mana rules till u int to mana ratio gets up.  Jade pieces of jewelry i think have hp and mana on em... another good thing for any casting class starting out.  PBB's are cheap and good, so is a Green Silken Drape and the extra stats on that rock when u have to melee (which is always for young necro).  other than that i would say get what u can afford.  When u get higher u can just go solo for anything u want, so equipment isnt hard to get.  hehe well that was long....so peace out.<br>&nbsp;<br>Fendrish 48 Barb War<br>Deadinc 38 Iksar Necro<br>Zebriz 12 Iksar Shaman</td></tr>
