	   <tr><td colspan=2>Burning Woods is your friend.<br><br>You can solo there till 56.  You will have to kill greens in order to get blues to pop, though.  <br><br>There is a sweet place on the Western Wall South of the Giant Fort across from the crater.  Pull to the small clearing by the zone wall.  Nice stuff goes into the valley between the wall and the crater.  Stuff dies much faster here then in SkyFire and you get more loot cause of it.  You can get spells off the Wurms, Forest Giant Anciennes, Sarnak Zealots, Moldering Gorillas, Tatterback Gorillas(I think), Scoriae Hornets and maybe the highest level skeletons.<br><br>You need JBoots to do this or SOW potions.<br><br>Be careful when exploring this area as there are some mobs that are KOS to a DE necro.  And DO NOT under ANY circumstances try to solo Gullerback.  He will eat you up.<br><br>The rest you can figure out.  Good luck!<br><br>Ishtarra Gemeinseele<br>Warlock on Tunare Server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
