	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok, I am a newbie, and keep seeing all this talk about kiting, and quad kiting, etc...<br>Eh?  What is it?<br>I understand some of the game's terminology, like tanks, and pulling, but this one is new to me.  :(<br><br>Joji<br>Dark-Elf Necromancer <br>Level 6<br>Xev Server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
